    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DISCLAIMER:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Tales of: Sena (Legacy)&quot; is the old, not continued version of &quot;Tales of: Sena&quot;,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legacy is the first project by CloudWork Studio, the first step towards the big story that will be &quot;Tales of: Sena&quot;!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the foundations that formed the To:S we love and cherrish today.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Old Story and Lore are not accurate anymore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters and their Designs are not accurate anymore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Old Dates and Promises don't count anymore</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310180/extras/29f75d6210e82a2678a667b99e104968.avif?t=1772184461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310180/extras_big/29f75d6210e82a2678a667b99e104968.avif?t=1772184461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎(<i>Froggy and Clarice are watching)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE THE STORY:</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tales of: Sena (Legacy) is an Exploration/ Story type game, where you take the role</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >of the young girl Sena in the loved top down angle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🡲 Walk through a beautiful 8bit pixel world and explore/ interact with objects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🡲 Start a talk with unique characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >most of them will even talk back...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🡲 Look at the environment, Sena will always have something to say about it</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WEIRD MINIGAMES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🡲 A CHALLENGING PLATFORMER WITH MANY LEVELS TO EXPLORE!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🡲 A CLICKER TYCOON!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🡲 WORKING IN-GAME TV!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🡲 EVEN A DATING SIMULATOR!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...wait what?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THERE ARE A LOT OF PLACES TO EXPLORE:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Woods</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ Beautiful nature with a lot of green!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ A lot of nice people live there too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ With a cool frog somewhere as well...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310180/extras/5358cd0acd4c2c77b0a2e5b4a2abe707.avif?t=1772184461\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Family House</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ Very colorful and a happy place!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ Good and bad memories are everywhere!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ With a locked shed in the garden!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310180/extras/9f2ed206487ac63dbc889c136c384d38.avif?t=1772184461\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Hub</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ Balances the life beyond!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ Soulworms love it here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➜ A dirty and useless whole!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Trust me)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310180/extras/ac160dbc20de67cfa0b2d0a3a8b716ae.avif?t=1772184461\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p>",
